  m_text: "She turns to her sister, desperately trying to signal something, but her
    body won\u2019t cooperate. It seems Alice is having the same struggles. They
    watch helplessly as the walls close in around them, the Cat\u2019s cold voice
    pressing down on them like weighted chains. \r\n"
