  m_text: "They continue to walk forward following the chattery cat. \n\nAs he talks
    the room begins to warp and turn, it feels weird, something is off.\n\r\nThey
    girls try to focus on what he\u2019s saying but even the voice has faded into
    a static noise. \n"
