  m_text: "\rBoth girls feel stuck to the floor. The cat continues to walk forward
    unperturbed by their troubles.  \n\r\nHis voice gets sickly sweet, talking about
    new playthings and how it\u2019s been so long since someone has chosen him. He
    sounds excited, like a kid on Christmas morning.\r\n\r\n\n"
